Andy Flower resumes as wicket-keeper at 169/1 after 28 overs.
ME Trescothick 100 in 155 mins off 89 balls, 11x4, 1x6
Zimbabwe were fined 2 overs for a slow over rate

stories.title: England overwhelm Zimbabwe after Trescothick century
stories.summary: Left-handed opener Marcus Trescothick was at his belligerent best on Wednesday afternoon, crashing his second consecutive one-day century to pave the way for a massive 108-run English victory
